relevant_findings.general: Thin elderly lying in bed in no acute distress
relevant_findings.ent: Ears and nose without visible erythema; oropharynx without visible lesion, erythema or exudate; missing teeth, no dentures in place
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Heart regular, no murmur, no S3, no S4, no JVD
relevant_findings.respiratory: Lungs clear to auscultation with quiet breath sounds (limited by poor participation with exam), breathing is non-labored
relevant_findings.gastrointestinal: Abdomen soft, non-distended, mildly tender to deep palpation in suprapubic area, bowel sounds quiet, no HSM
relevant_findings.gu: No suprapubic fullness, foley in place draining clear yellow
relevant_findings.musculoskeletal: Neck supple, moves all extremities, strength testing limited by poor participation with exam
relevant_findings.skin: No obvious rashes or ulcerations noted, right hip without erythema or ecchymosis, no induration or fluctuance appreciated, mild tenderness to palpation
relevant_findings.neuro: Alert, oriented, face symmetric, minimal speech just answers yes or no, hard of hearing (hears best through right ear), moves all limbs
